{"heading":"The Saints gain fellowship with God by obedience—We must confess our sins to gain forgiveness.","number":1,"verseCount":10,"verses":[[1,[["That",["study-note-ref","a",["JST 1 Jn. 1:1 Brethren, this is the testimony which we give of that which was from the beginning …"]]]," which was from the ",["beginning",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 1:2 (1–4, 14)","nt/john/1.2"],"."]]],", which we have heard, which we have seen with our eyes, which we have looked upon, and our hands have handled, of the ",["Word of life",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Jesus Christ, Messenger of the Covenant","tg/jesus-christ-messenger-of-the-covenant"],"."]]],";"]],[2,["(For the life was manifested, and we have seen ",["it,",["clarity-word"]]," and bear witness, and ",["shew",["study-note-ref","a",["GR declare, announce, bring tidings."]]]," unto you that ",["eternal life",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 17:3","nt/john/17.3"],"; ",["1 Jn. 5:20","nt/1-jn/5.20"],"."]]],", which was with the Father, and was manifested unto us;)"]],[3,["That which we have ",["seen",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Witness","tg/witness"],"."]]]," and heard declare we unto you, that ye also may have fellowship with us: and truly our ",["fellowship",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Fellowshipping","tg/fellowshipping"],"."]]]," ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," with the ",["Father",["study-note-ref","c",[["Moses 6:68","pgp/moses/6.68"],"."]]],", and with his Son Jesus Christ."]],[4,["And these things ",["write",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Scriptures, Writing of","tg/scriptures-writing-of"],"."]]]," we unto you, that your joy may be full."]],[5,["This then is the message which we have heard of him, and declare unto you, that God is ",["light",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 8:12","nt/john/8.12"],". ",["TG God, Perfection of","tg/god-perfection-of"],"; ",["Light [noun]","tg/light-noun"],"."]]],", and in him is no ",["darkness",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Darkness, Spiritual","tg/darkness-spiritual"],"; ",["Walking in Darkness","tg/wa